{"tid":2348875,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：離任不四散  Cable同學會解總辭之謎（李八方）","createTime":"2021-01-01T06:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T06:01:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cde1f35556702f064a7888dffe82fecf7a1a46","tid":2348875,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:01:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/RH37VPTMBZHXDN76D5B7RUV23U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FRH37VPTMBZHXDN76D5B7RUV23U%2F&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhXG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=9c8fc761\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FRH37VPTMBZHXDN76D5B7RUV23U%2F&h=f2cfb00d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/RH37VPTMBZHXDN76D5B7RUV23U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：離任不四散 <br />\nCable同學會解總辭之謎（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0GFmnWKYa3wb2PewXcxyc5_q7UQ=/1800x1485/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B7W6ED75XVFVLAIC6T2FNL5S54.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0GFmnWKYa3wb2PewXcxyc5_q7UQ%3D%2F1800x1485%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB7W6ED75XVFVLAIC6T2FNL5S54.gif&h=f2a8a07b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線新聞台月初大地震，40人被裁，觸發多位記者、採訪主任辭職，有線中國組更加總辭明志，成組人做埋今日就正式離開，代表住有線新聞一個時代嘅終結。<br />\n<br />\n不過，唔代表舊有線新聞嘅班底同埋快樂新聞部就此四散，一班有線新聞嘅前員工、就快離開嘅員工，日前喺facebook成立咗一個專頁，叫做「Cable同學會」，記錄呢個新聞部嘅點滴，仲搵埋有線好多猛料舊人撐場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n趙應春彈台歌贈興<br />\n<br />\n呢個專頁邀請曾經喺有線新聞部工作嘅人，。。。。。。。。。。，仲有前有線前高級記者吳婉君爆採訪主任曾楚群嘅上位之謎。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。，而「Cable同學會」頭炮就會由有線中國組總採訪主任司徒元講述有線新聞嘅價值同埋中國組總辭嘅因由，八方好期待快啲有得睇。<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vi3hcAO0SW8TAFvec49yQsBkEBQ=/1578x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MZZMHPYT2RE75ABBXDIHIB7V4Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fvi3hcAO0SW8TAFvec49yQsBkEBQ%3D%2F1578x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMZZMHPYT2RE75ABBXDIHIB7V4Y.jpg&h=e0da75dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■司徒元將會負責「Cable同學會」頭炮video，講返點解要總辭同埋有線新聞嘅價值。"}]}